  "detailed_description": "Gordy and the Monster Moon is a bite-sized exploration-driven game about a pumpkin astronaut going on spooky adventures.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore the strange and varied biomes of the Monster Moon!<br></li><li>Find upgrades and unlock shortcuts to help you explore even better!<br></li><li>Defend yourself from monsters with a cobweb you found on the ground.<br></li><li>Ask dad for help if you get stuck!<br></li><li>What <i>is</i> in Lander B?</li></ul>",
